'''R. N. Abhyankar''' (dates unknown) was an Indian [[first-class cricket]]er active 1961–1968 who played for [[Vidarbha cricket team|Vidarbha]]. He made 15 appearances, scoring 467 [[run (cricket)|runs]] with a highest score of 73, and took ten [[wicket]]s with a best [[innings]] return of three for 47.<ref name=CI>[http://www.espncricinfo.com/ci/content/player/26608.html R. N. Abhyankar at ESPNcricinfo]</ref><ref name=CA>[https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Players/38/38026/38026.html R. N. Abhyankar at CricketArchive]</ref>
